00:06:27.584 --> 00:06:28.500
So that's interesting.

00:06:28.500 --> 00:06:30.180
We've been able to
relate these two

00:06:30.180 --> 00:06:33.550
things to these kind of
two arbitrarily lengths.

00:06:33.550 --> 00:06:36.720
But we need to somehow connect
