00:07:37.630 --> 00:07:39.350
We can say that
this thing is going

00:07:39.350 --> 00:07:41.467
to be the same
thing as this thing.

00:07:41.467 --> 00:07:43.050
Or another way you
could have said it,

00:07:43.050 --> 00:07:46.610
is you could have said, well,
