00:08:29.310 --> 00:08:32.730
That's our focal length.

00:08:32.730 --> 00:08:35.630
As f in this triangle is
related to this length

00:08:35.630 --> 00:08:37.250
on this triangle.

00:08:37.250 --> 00:08:41.470
They are both opposite
