So we got d naught, or d0
I guess we'd call it, to di

00:09:22.290 --> 00:09:24.990
is equal to the ratio
of the focal length

00:09:24.990 --> 00:09:28.440
to the difference of
the image distance

00:09:28.440 --> 00:09:32.290
to the-- the focal
